docs\progress\logs\20260625-035825_execute-P001.log:1869:Hmm, it seems the future UI might need to handle cases where there's an error and no plan available. I could consider including a `path` or `filePath` field to make things clearer. Having this in mind could really help ensure that all necessary information is being returned and makes it easier to troubleshoot in the UI. I'll need to keep these requirements in check as I finalize the structure. It feels like covering all bases is the right approach!
